text: Jingan may refer to: *Jing'an County (靖安县), in Jiangxi, People's Republic of China *Jing'an District (静安区), in Shanghai, PRC *Jing'an Temple (静安寺), in Shanghai, PRC *Jingan Station (景安站), station of the Taipei Metro, in New Taipei, Taiwan *Jing'an, Changli County (靖安镇), town in Changli County, Hebei, PRC
title: Jingan
